{
  "stem": "18294.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 204.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But the doctor there, you don't need it really for a doctor, like you need for the-- you need antibiotics, like something like that, what didn't-- there was no antibiotic-- but something what protect you, needed money to buy.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a hospital, but not for very, very sick people.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Very, very sick people, they would get killed.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because the German used to come and check.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Not really.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Most of them, I think, the older people, you know, the older people.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The ghetto, really didn't arrive-- to our ghetto, didn't come nowhere from other places, only Vilna, only from the town.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There used to be ghettos where they used to bring from-- from another part, from Poland.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, they didn't bring to our ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To our ghetto was only Vilna.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So every time there was less and less and less.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Deportation start approximately, like in-- this was in 1943, in September-- it was the 23rd of September.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Why I remember so good the day?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because every time it's coming the [NON-ENGLISH] from the liquidation from ghetto is the 23rd of September 1943.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Then the liquid-- there was not many people already left in Vilna ghetto.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But still there was enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then they bring us to a field in-- in Vilna.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "That was already prepared for us with-- with gates closed up.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we was there maybe a couple of nights, something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It was cold and rainy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then they start to select us to go out from the-- from there.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they select us right and left.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "This was the liquidation from the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I was going together with my mother and mother-in-law, keep them together.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And when we come to the gate, the German was standing.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
